name: Limited Edition Screen-printed JAMboree Poster
description:
11x17 Screen-printed Jamboree 2011 Poster

Design by: Mike Adams 

Limited supplies, first come / first serve. Each are individually numbered and stamped for approval. 

Please print out PayPal email confirmation receipt and present it at The Jamboree's merchandise booth on April 9th. 

If you want this poster but you cannot make it to the event, please email TheJamboreeOhio@gmail.com to arrange payment/shipping plans.

Payment will be processed by GOAHEADINC.

name: Jamboree Backpack
description:
There will not be lockers available to store all of your stuff! So, you'll need one of these if you plan on picking up any merchandise at the Jamboree!

Simple and comfortable drawstring backpack. A white jamboree logo is printed on the outside of the bag. 

If ordered online, please print out the paypal email receipt you receive and present it to the Jamboree Merchandise booth on April 9th to redeem it for your item(s).

Limited supplies available!

name: Jamboree T-Shirt (white)
description:
The official 2011 Jamboree T-shirt in WHITE.

Sizes run:

Small 
Medium
Large
XL
2XL

Printed on 100% combed cotton. 

**Includes a full back print of the lineup and festival information.

Available for PICKUP at the Jamboree on April 9th. Please visit the Merch Guy's booth with a valid form of Identity (Drivers Licence, School ID, ect.) AND a printed paypal receipt to claim your shirt.

Payments are processed by "GOAHEAD INC". 

If you have any questions, please email us at thejamboreeohio@gmail.com
